  <brief_title>Value of FLT PET/CT in Radium-223 Therapy of mCRPC Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Value of FLT PET/CT in Radium-223 Therapy of Patients With Metastatic Castration-resistant Prostate Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
